description: The comprehensive redevelopment of the Lewisham Retail Park and Nos. 66  76 Loampit Vale including the demolition of all buildings on site to facilitate the provision of 4,343sqm of non-residential floorspace comprising (A1) Shops, (A2) Financial & Professional Services, (A3) Restaurants & Cafés, (B1) Business, (D1) Non-Residential Institutions and (D2) Assembly & Leisure uses and 536 residential units in buildings ranging from 4  24 storeys in height with private and communal open spaces, on-site energy centre, car and cycle parking, and associated landscaping and public realm works.
